> <div class="border-white/10 relative h-full w-2 border-r" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6></div> <div class="border-white/10 relative h-full w-2 border-l" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6></div> </div> </section> <!-- Spacer --> <section class="relative" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="border-white/10 border-y" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-2" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="mx-px h-16 lg:h-24" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6></div> </div> </div> <div aria-hidden="true" class="border-white/10 pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 mx-auto flex max-w-7xl justify-between border-x" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="border-white/10 relative h-full w-2 border-r" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6></div> <div class="border-white/10 relative h-full w-2 border-l" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6></div> </div> </section> <section id="reviews" class="relative" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="border-white/10 border-y" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-2" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="bg-black mx-px" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <!-- Header --> <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl space-y-4 text-center py-16" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <span class="text-white font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-wider" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>Community</span> <h2 class="text-white mt-6 text-balance text-4xl font-semibold lg:text-5xl" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>People love building with CORSPROXY</h2> <p class="text-gray-400 text-balance text-lg" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>Discover why developers choose CORSPROXY every day.</p> </div> <!-- Testimonials Grid --> <div class="bg-white/10 grid gap-px sm:grid-cols-2 sm:grid-rows-4 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-rows-3 *:bg-black *:rounded" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <!-- Featured: Microsoft --> <a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/answers/questions/925517/create-a-choropleth-map" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="row-start-1 flex flex-col justify-between gap-8 p-8 lg:col-start-1 !bg-[#111113] transition-transform duration-200 hover:scale-[1.02]" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="space-y-6" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="flex items-start justify-between" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <img src="/images/customers/microsoft.svg" alt="Microsoft Logo" class="h-6 w-auto brightness-0 invert" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="size-5 text-white opacity-50" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M15.75 2.25H21a.75.75 0 0 1 .75.75v5.25a.75.75 0 0 1-1.5 0V4.81L8.03 17.03a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06-1.06L19.19 3.75h-3.44a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.5Zm-10.5 4.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-1.5 1.5v10.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5 1.5h10.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5-1.5V10.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.5 0v8.25a3 3 0 0 1-3 3H5.25a3 3 0 0 1-3-3V8.25a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h8.25a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5H5.25Z" clip-rule="evenodd" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6></path> </svg> </div> <p class="text-balance text-lg text-white" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>"I'm using corsproxy.io for fetching geojson files from azure cloud."</p> </div> <div class="flex items-center gap-3" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="ring-white/10 aspect-square size-9 overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-md shadow-black/15 ring-1" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6><img alt="Ricky Brundritt" class="h-full w-full object-cover" width="460" height="460" loading="lazy" src="/images/testimonials/rickly-brund.png" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6></div> <div class="space-y-px" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <p class="text-sm font-medium text-white" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>Ricky Brundritt</p> <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>Microsoft Geospatial Architect</p> </div> </div> </a> <!-- Card 1 --> <a href="https://w3.cs.jmu.edu/mayfiecs/cs343/notes/wk10/0403/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="flex flex-col justify-end gap-8 p-8 transition-transform duration-200 hover:scale-[1.02]" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <p class="text-white self-end text-balance text-lg" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>"If you are getting an error saying something about "CORS" or "origin": There's a free "CORS Proxy" at corsproxy.io you can use."</p> <div class="flex items-center gap-3" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="ring-white/10 aspect-square size-9 overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-md shadow-black/15 ring-1" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6><img alt="Chris Mayfield" class="h-full w-full object-cover" width="460" height="460" loading="lazy" src="/images/testimonials/mayfiecs.jpg" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6></div> <div class="space-y-px" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <p class="text-sm font-medium text-white" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>Chris Mayfield</p> <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>Professor, James Madison University</p> </div> </div> </a> <!-- Card 2 --> <a href="https://discuss.layer5.io/t/yet-another-hack-dealing-with-cors-issues-in-reactjs/3984" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="flex flex-col justify-end gap-8 p-8 transition-transform duration-200 hover:scale-[1.02]" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <p class="text-white self-end text-balance text-lg" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>"I recently discovered a simple and effective solution that can save you a lot of time and frustration. It’s called Corsproxy. "</p> <div class="flex items-center gap-3" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="ring-white/10 aspect-square size-9 overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-md shadow-black/15 ring-1" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6><img alt="Ajaezo Kingsley" class="h-full w-full object-cover" width="460" height="460" loading="lazy" src="/images/testimonials/ajaezo-kingsley.jpg" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6></div> <div class="space-y-px" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <p class="text-sm font-medium text-white" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>Ajaezo Kingsley</p> <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>Senior Software Engineer</p> </div> </div> </a> <!-- Card 3 --> <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/posts/koushikbajpayee07_reactjs-webdevelopment-frontenddevelopment-activity-7382282501018255360-YvR9" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="flex flex-col justify-end gap-8 p-8 transition-transform duration-200 hover:scale-[1.02]" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <p class="text-white self-end text-balance text-lg" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>"I used corsproxy.io to safely bypass CORS restrictions while testing from localhost. "</p> <div class="flex items-center gap-3" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="ring-white/10 aspect-square size-9 overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-md shadow-black/15 ring-1" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6><img alt="Koushik Bajpayee" class="h-full w-full object-cover" width="460" height="460" loading="lazy" src="/images/testimonials/koushik.jpg" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6></div> <div class="space-y-px" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <p class="text-sm font-medium text-white" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>Koushik Bajpayee</p> <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>Full-Stack Software Developer</p> </div> </div> </a> <!-- Card 4 --> <div class="flex flex-col justify-end gap-8 p-8 transition-transform duration-200 hover:scale-[1.02]" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <p class="text-white self-end text-balance text-lg" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>"Client-side access of HTTP resources is in many cases broken. That is why services like corsproxy.io exist."</p> <div class="flex items-center gap-3" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="ring-white/10 aspect-square size-9 overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-md shadow-black/15 ring-1" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6><img alt="Glodie Lukose" class="h-full w-full object-cover" width="460" height="460" loading="lazy" src="/images/testimonials/martynas.jpg" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6></div> <div class="space-y-px" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <p class="text-sm font-medium text-white" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>Martynas Jusevicius</p> <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>Co-founder & CTO of AtomGraph</p> </div> </div> </div> <!-- Featured: Google --> <a href="https://support.google.com/docs/thread/330430447?hl=en&msgid=330794758" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="row-start-3 flex flex-col justify-between gap-8 p-8 sm:col-start-2 lg:row-start-2 !bg-[#111113] transition-transform duration-200 hover:scale-[1.02]" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="space-y-6" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="flex items-start justify-between" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <img src="/images/customers/google.svg" alt="Google Logo" class="h-8 w-auto brightness-0 invert" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="size-5 text-white opacity-50" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M15.75 2.25H21a.75.75 0 0 1 .75.75v5.25a.75.75 0 0 1-1.5 0V4.81L8.03 17.03a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06-1.06L19.19 3.75h-3.44a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.5Zm-10.5 4.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-1.5 1.5v10.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5 1.5h10.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5-1.5V10.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.5 0v8.25a3 3 0 0 1-3 3H5.25a3 3 0 0 1-3-3V8.25a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h8.25a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5H5.25Z" clip-rule="evenodd" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6></path> </svg> </div> <p class="text-balance text-lg text-white" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>"I recommend CORSPROXY to anyone in Google community who is having issues with CORS."</p> </div> <div class="flex items-center gap-3" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="ring-white/10 aspect-square size-9 overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-md shadow-black/15 ring-1" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6><img alt="Shadcn" class="h-full w-full object-cover" width="460" height="460" loading="lazy" src="/images/testimonials/hyde.jpg" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6></div> <div class="space-y-px" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <p class="text-sm font-medium text-white" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>--Hyde</p> <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>Diamond Product Expert</p> </div> </div> </a> <!-- Card 5 --> <a href="https://x.com/matthewsmith/status/1810883502771949748?s=20" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="flex flex-col justify-end gap-8 p-8 transition-transform duration-200 hover:scale-[1.02]" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <p class="text-white self-end text-balance text-lg" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>"It is awesome that CORS Proxy exists. I recommend corsproxy.io."</p> <div class="flex items-center gap-3" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="ring-white/10 aspect-square size-9 overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-md shadow-black/15 ring-1" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6><img alt="Matt" class="h-full w-full object-cover" width="460" height="460" loading="lazy" src="/images/testimonials/matt.jpg" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6></div> <div class="space-y-px" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <p class="text-sm font-medium text-white" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>Matt</p> <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>Founder, Section Star</p> </div> </div> </a> <!-- Card 6 --> <a href="https://x.com/AikasRoni/status/1886471996877234258?s=20" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="flex flex-col justify-end gap-8 p-8 transition-transform duration-200 hover:scale-[1.02]" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <p class="text-white self-end text-balance text-lg" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>"Next, you may encounter CORS errors...prefix this "https://corsproxy.io?" in front of your image url."</p> <div class="flex items-center gap-3" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="ring-white/10 aspect-square size-9 overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-md shadow-black/15 ring-1" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6><img alt="MengChi Chang" class="h-full w-full object-cover" width="460" height="460" loading="lazy" src="/images/testimonials/mengchi.jpg" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6></div> <div class="space-y-px" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <p class="text-sm font-medium text-white" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>MengChi Chang</p> <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>Product Designer</p> </div> </div> </a> <!-- Featured: DCU --> <a href="https://humphryscomputing.com/Notes/Networks/ajax.more.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="flex flex-col justify-between gap-8 p-8 sm:row-start-2 lg:col-start-3 lg:row-start-3 !bg-[#111113] transition-transform duration-200 hover:scale-[1.02]" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="space-y-6" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <img src="/images/customers/dcu.png" alt="DCU Logo" class="h-9 w-auto brightness-0 invert" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <p class="text-balance text-lg text-white" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>"Even if the server does not cooperate, you can use a CORS proxy like corsproxy.io to fetch arbitrary resources off the Internet"</p> </div> <div class="flex items-center gap-3" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="ring-white/10 aspect-square size-9 overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-md shadow-black/15 ring-1" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6><img alt="Dr. Mark Humphrys" class="h-full w-full object-cover" width="460" height="460" loading="lazy" src="/images/testimonials/humphrys.jpg" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6></div> <div class="space-y-px" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <p class="text-sm font-medium text-white" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>Dr. Mark Humphrys</p> <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>Professor, Dublin City University</p> </div> </div> </a> </div> </div> </div> </div> <!-- Vertical lines --> <div aria-hidden="true" class="border-white/10 pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 mx-auto flex max-w-7xl justify-between border-x" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="border-white/10 relative h-full w-2 border-r" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6></div> <div class="border-white/10 relative h-full w-2 border-l" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6></div> </div> </section> <!-- Stats Map Section --> <section class="relative" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="border-white/10 border-y" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-2" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="mx-px" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <section class="py-12 md:py-20"> <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6"> <div><img class="[mask-image:linear-gradient(to_bottom,transparent,black_35%,black_75%,transparent)]" alt="tailark stats map" loading="lazy" src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,%3Csvg%20viewBox%3D%220%200%20116%2055%22%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20style%3D%22background-color%3A%20transparent%22%3E%0A%20%20